snippet.title: Angry Birds Friends official launch trailer
snippet.description:
The official launch trailer for Angry Birds Friends. http://friends.angrybirds.com

Play Angry Birds Friends on Facebook from today. Compete with your friends in weekly tournaments to win power-ups. New levels to play each week!
